## Engenharia de Software e Privacidade

5. **A Framework to Support Software Developers in Implementing Privacy Features**  
   *Mazeli, C. (2022).*  
   ACM.  
   [Acessar artigo](https://dl.acm.org/doi/abs/10.1145/3510454.3517054?casa_token=FZmDeLqYuZ8AAAAA:aszniR2DkBBzeRoJjGKJicnoVj1ZWab0aN3luDtRmRRz2pbswPbGA4yidBEa5gvG44bbPLJnqb4Yim4)

