   *Fatima, A.; Funke, T.; Lago, P. (2025).*  
   Relatório Técnico.  
   [Acessar artigo](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TL1_LuE_xZ7xZ2cU-WfP7mHIoifdulY1/view)

7. **An Exploratory Study of Productivity Perceptions in Software Teams**  
