   [Acessar artigo](https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/9474787?casa_token=fgTm1Hw-Z1MAAAAA:taaME1CJyInLpQvKe2PEPBgkL9zxXHjGLOhJy2vT0E-WSQ8zxQwddOT8m5P40tQOsc42GCQUxLOd)

